diff:1372654782:1372654766:=54a55,59%0a> You may gain a total of up to +10 Incentive XP at creation (+5 for General Incentive XP and +5 from Werewolf Incentive XP). See the guidelines here:%0a> *[[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=250&t=32374|General Incentive XP]]%0a> *[[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=454&t=34024|Werewolf Incentive XP]]%0a> %0a> To apply Incentive XP, simply go over the limit of General XP by that equivalent amount. For instance, if you are using 8 Incentive XP, go ahead and spend XP until you are at -8 General XP on your character sheet. ''You should be clear about why you think you deserve Incentive XP'': document what you are aiming to get the bonuses from in your Notes field.%0a
