diff:1372654766:1372654655:=34,45c34,45%0a%3c Please consult the [[O/R/B Book List]] to see what books you may draw material from.%0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Renown:''' %0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Rituals:''' %0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Fetishes:''' %0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Lodges:''' %0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Territory (including Locus), Totem & Pack Tactics:''' %0a%3c %0a---%0a> Please consult the [[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=321&t=32346|O/R/B Book List]] to see what books you may draw material from.%0a> %0a> *'''Renown:''' Renown at 3 costs one restricted slot. You may not start with Renown at 4 or higher.%0a> %0a> *'''Rituals:''' Rituals 3 costs one restricted slot and is the maximum that starting characters may have, except Ithaeur; Ithaeur may start with up to Rituals 4, but this costs a total of two restricted slots.%0a> %0a> *'''Fetishes:''' Every new Fetish taken after the first one costs one restricted slot; otherwise, there are no special rules. ''Example: one level 3 Fetish is no restricted slots. One level 2 Fetish and one level 1 Fetish comes to 1 restricted slot.''%0a> %0a> *'''Lodges:''' Characters who meet the pre-requisites may start on a Lodge; this requires one restricted slot.%0a> %0a> *'''Territory (including Locus), Totem & Pack Tactics:''' These are only available at creation to characters who start with a pack; if your character is packless, you must first join a pack and then acquire them.%0a> %0a47,49c47,49%0a%3c **'''Language (First Tongue):''' %0a%3c %0a%3c **'''Allies (Local Spirits), Contacts (Local Spirits), etc.:''' %0a---%0a> **'''Language (First Tongue):''' Werewolves who belong to a Tribe do not need this Merit; in other words, if you belong to a Tribe at character creation, but you forget to add this Merit to your sheet, it is still assumed your character can speak & write in the First Tongue. Ghost Wolves must still purchase it, however. (I'll admit that my motivation here is as much to save us STs the effort of post-sanction corrections as anything else... -MarcD)%0a> %0a> **'''Allies (Local Spirits), Contacts (Local Spirits), etc.:''' These are banned at character creation, but may be acquired IC.%0a
